{"tid":389192,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[IT狗老師課室] 30秒教你將學校email自動轉寄去個人email","createTime":"2017-09-06T04:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T10:33:39.000Z","uid":133747,"like":52,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae65a3721dcc69110ddd8e0fcf46ba9e2ea75748","tid":389192,"uid":133747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:41:20.000Z","msg":"大家好, 我係IT狗老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本來今日高高興興跑花田<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/102317_644b76bcc011d48bf3a33f845f0da93d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F102317_644b76bcc011d48bf3a33f845f0da93d.jpg&h=577413af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跑到一半收到朋友電話問野, 藍瘦香菇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個種失落就好似打機打到一半比人打斷左咁, 你明唔明呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/102941_a919938479e5b3815a38f471f73b8546.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F102941_a919938479e5b3815a38f471f73b8546.jpg&h=2abaad61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然要教, 不如一次過教大家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">跟足以下步驟嘅話, 以後學校email收到嘅野會自動轉寄去個人email, 咁就唔洗成日check咁麻煩啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家我用vtc outlook示範一下, 其他email system嘅做法大致相同<br />\n<br />\n1. 登入你個email<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/111642_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F111642_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=de9dce0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 禁左上角粒禁左上角粒[齒輪], 再禁左下角嘅[郵件]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/112451_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F112451_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=0f51bc46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 禁左上角粒禁左上角嘅[收件匣和整理規則], 再禁格黎嘅[ + ]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/113448_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F113448_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=26478fa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 重頭戲嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n名稱: 打[Send To My Email]<br />\n當電郵送達xxx時: 揀[套用到所有郵件]<br />\n執行下列所有動作: 揀[轉寄xxx或傳送] &gt; [將郵件給轉寄] &gt; 打[個人email](CDROM@LIGHK.COM只係示範) &gt; [儲存]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/114615_09dd8c2662b96ce14928333f055c5580.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F114615_09dd8c2662b96ce14928333f055c5580.png&h=46fe0f90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/121544_8266e4bfeda1bd42d8f9794eb4ea0a13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F121544_8266e4bfeda1bd42d8f9794eb4ea0a13.png&h=c78556f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 如果你做齊應該係咁樣, 禁[確定], 搞掂! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/122929_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F122929_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png&h=6e0e77a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> IT狗, 你的資訊真的很有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老師我睇唔明呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後祝各位新一年GPA坐3爆4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3cd1fb89b1fc5635f9124a3f1cf7eafbfde392f","tid":389192,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:53:20.000Z","msg":"冇乜用<br />\nadd多個account睇all inboxes仲爽"},{"pid":"c98bd0dc293454cfc194084671a4824132bd4535","tid":389192,"uid":1880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:56:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇乜用<br />\nadd多個account睇all inboxes仲爽</blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"001efc0ec595abd5bee911ff7e8f8ff44465927a","tid":389192,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T04:58:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8998cbb605b944c88c2fb2a47c50f36d4d5b5e77","tid":389192,"uid":45055,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T10:06:01.000Z","msg":"藍你老母 大陸狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15651bc890186311d1790545a8803d8b4ce1a61b","tid":389192,"uid":108247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T18:08:59.000Z","msg":"每日幾百個junk mail   不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78e8b7f8810fd8562f3bb4e743954e26ff08f23","tid":389192,"uid":95305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T01:23:03.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"6ea4ff831593c1c83cbdc114c54b42f9c02e2301","tid":389192,"uid":84177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/013815_04d0a729550c69dd6ccfa4015841bbf0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-